01:31:04.823 --> 01:31:10.455
Muslim preachers from Dhaka are
going around stirring up the peasants.

01:31:10.996 --> 01:31:12.623
Have you heard about it?

01:31:13.765 --> 01:31:15.665
l've read about it in the papers.

01:31:15.767 --> 01:31:18.600
What's to stop them from coming here?

01:31:19.538 --> 01:31:22.371
-- Nothing.
-- And then?

01:31:24.276 --> 01:31:26.141
But if anything does happen,

01:31:27.045 --> 01:31:31.379
can we place all the blame
on the preachers?

01:31:32.217 --> 01:31:34.344
We are also responsible.

01:31:35.120 --> 01:31:37.213
How can we just ignore that?

01:31:38.790 --> 01:31:41.953
Think about how we ourselves
have treated the poor Muslims.

01:31:43.095 --> 01:31:47.293
Have we even respected
their rights as human beings?

01:31:47.399 --> 01:31:50.994
That's true, but what
can be done about it now?

01:31:54.606 --> 01:31:55.834
l'll go there.

01:31:57.709 --> 01:31:59.939
l want to see for myself.

01:32:01.113 --> 01:32:03.809
Rumors can be misleading.

01:32:03.915 --> 01:32:07.578
Nikhil, can't you inform the magistrate?

01:32:08.253 --> 01:32:10.847
l don't think he'd mind a riot.

01:32:11.656 --> 01:32:13.954
lt's an easy way for him
to see the Swadeshi punished.

01:32:14.059 --> 01:32:16.527
There is one thing you can do.

01:32:18.530 --> 01:32:21.556
You can at least eradicate
the source of the trouble.

01:32:22.434 --> 01:32:24.868
Why let Sandip stay?

01:32:32.310 --> 01:32:35.177
l thought he'd leave of his own accord.

01:32:38.150 --> 01:32:39.549
But now --

01:32:40.252 --> 01:32:42.584
Leave? Why would he?

01:32:43.722 --> 01:32:46.919
