Remember this?

01:36:47.198 --> 01:36:49.792
lt's from my soap factory.

01:36:54.639 --> 01:36:58.131
You saved it?
-- Not just the soap.

01:37:00.445 --> 01:37:04.176
Towels, pens, matches.
l kept everything.

01:37:08.720 --> 01:37:10.244
Have you ever used it?

01:37:13.691 --> 01:37:18.253
lt's no good for anything,
not even for washing clothes.

01:37:24.369 --> 01:37:26.963
What foolish notions l had back then.

01:37:27.071 --> 01:37:28.766
