01:54:02.599 --> 01:54:04.226
Can't you guess?

01:54:05.502 --> 01:54:06.992
Money?

01:54:07.504 --> 01:54:11.031
So little? There can't be
more than 500 in those bags.

01:54:11.675 --> 01:54:15.042
You must have forgotten.
l asked for 5,000 rupees.

01:54:20.851 --> 01:54:22.443
What's this?

01:54:23.754 --> 01:54:24.948
Gold coins?

01:54:34.231 --> 01:54:35.562
Gold.

01:54:38.001 --> 01:54:40.231
Gold.

01:54:43.640 --> 01:54:45.904
You should have told me.

01:54:46.810 --> 01:54:48.937
How else would l know?

01:54:51.448 --> 01:54:53.439
Please don't be angry, my queen bee.

01:55:00.357 --> 01:55:03.622
-- l need to talk to you.
-- About what?

01:55:04.461 --> 01:55:07.089
l don't want you to stay here any longer.

01:55:07.197 --> 01:55:09.290
Things have taken a serious turn.

01:55:09.399 --> 01:55:12.027
Your presence may make matters worse.

01:55:13.136 --> 01:55:15.502
l want you to leave Sukhsayar
by tomorrow morning.

01:55:17.641 --> 01:55:20.337
Am l supposed to take orders from you?

01:55:20.444 --> 01:55:21.911
lt's not that.

01:55:23.313 --> 01:55:26.180
lf you leave for Calcutta,
it will be good for you,

01:55:27.084 --> 01:55:28.551
and for Sukhsayar as well.

01:55:29.786 --> 01:55:33.244
-- l have no work to do in Calcutta.
-- All the more reason to go.

01:55:34.291 --> 01:55:36.851
You've done too much work here.

01:55:38.662 --> 01:55:41.460
Don't think l haven't been
informed of your activities.

01:55:42.299 --> 01:55:45.234
From setting fire to the peasants' barns
to sinking Mirjan's boat,

01:55:46.203 --> 01:55:48.797
l've been informed of everything.

01:55:50.073 --> 01:55:52.906
You speak of unity
between Hindus and Muslims,

01:55:53.644 --> 01:55:56.579
but, in fact, you oppress Muslims.

01:55:58.081 --> 01:56:00.311
l won't tolerate it anymore.

01:56:02.653 --> 01:56:05.144
l may not believe in Swadeshi,

01:56:06.156 --> 01:56:08.818
but l truly admire
some Swadeshi leaders.

01:56:09.927 --> 01:56:15.229
But l don't admire those
whose actions belie their words.

01:56:16.466 --> 01:56:19.060
You're not saving the country.
You're ruining it.

01:56:20.304 --> 01:56:23.273
l won't allow this to go on in my estate.

01:56:23.373 --> 01:56:27.002
There's only one person here
l'm prepared to obey.

01:56:29.279 --> 01:56:31.110
Queen bee...

01:56:31.615 --> 01:56:34.880
Do you want me to stay or not?

01:56:43.727 --> 01:56:45.251
Queen bee.

01:56:46.296 --> 01:56:48.594
l'm waiting for your answer.

01:56:50.233 --> 01:56:53.066
Do you want me to leave?

01:56:55.706 --> 01:56:57.674
Please tell me, queen bee.

01:56:59.209 --> 01:57:01.143
l've said what l came to say.

01:57:03.747 --> 01:57:06.113
l hope l won't have to repeat it.

01:57:10.721 --> 01:57:12.552
Queen bee.

01:57:14.825 --> 01:57:16.952
What's the matter with you?

01:57:20.697 --> 01:57:23.598
You suddenly --
-- ls Amulya in your room?

01:57:23.700 --> 01:57:25.565
-- Amulya?
-- Yes.

01:57:25.669 --> 01:57:26.693
Why?

01:57:26.803 --> 01:57:29.704
Send him to me. lt's urgent.

01:57:30.407 --> 01:57:33.035
Can't you tell me why?

01:57:33.343 --> 01:57:35.402
No, l'll tell Amulya.

01:57:35.512 --> 01:57:37.480
Please send him to me.

01:57:37.581 --> 01:57:39.640
lt's my request.

01:57:40.851 --> 01:57:42.580
Very well.

01:59:19.216 --> 01:59:20.615
Amulya?

01:59:23.053 --> 01:59:26.250
Can you do me a favor?
-- Of course. What is it?

01:59:26.356 --> 01:59:27.653
Go to Calcutta.

01:59:27.758 --> 01:59:30.556
You can take the morning train
and return in the evening.

01:59:30.660 --> 01:59:32.787
The money for the journey is in this box.

01:59:32.896 --> 01:59:35.956
-- What's this box?
-- lt's my jewelry box.

01:59:36.066 --> 01:59:39.729
l need 5,000 rupees. Sell some
of my jewelry and bring me the money.

01:59:39.836 --> 01:59:41.929
l don't need any jewelry.
l can get you the money.

01:59:42.038 --> 01:59:43.369
How?

01:59:43.473 --> 01:59:46.408
This is not a small amount
we're talking about.

01:59:46.510 --> 01:59:47.875
l'll get it.

01:59:47.978 --> 01:59:50.105
No, do as l tell you.

01:59:50.714 --> 01:59:53.683
But why did you give
Mr. Sandip 5,000 rupees?

01:59:53.784 --> 01:59:55.649
He said he needed that much.

01:59:55.752 --> 01:59:59.449
No, according to our calculations,
we only needed 3,500.

01:59:59.556 --> 02:00:01.956
lf you give him more,
he spends it on himself.

02:00:02.726 --> 02:00:06.526
He's quite a spender.
He always travels first--class.

02:00:07.631 --> 02:00:09.690
-- Sandip?
-- Yes, sister.

02:00:09.800 --> 02:00:13.668
He says hardship saps a leader's strength.

02:00:14.504 --> 02:00:17.769
Well, l can't take back
what l've already given.

02:00:17.874 --> 02:00:20.707
He might need it in the future.
You get me the 5,000.

02:00:21.311 --> 02:00:24.678
Put the box away.
l'll get you the money tonight.

02:00:24.781 --> 02:00:26.715
-- How?
-- From the treasury.

02:00:27.717 --> 02:00:31.016
Are you insane?
What about the guards?

02:00:31.121 --> 02:00:33.146
We carry weapons, sister.

02:00:41.097 --> 02:00:43.258
Good heavens!

02:00:43.967 --> 02:00:46.026
Why are you upset, sister?

02:00:46.136 --> 02:00:48.229
We need funding
to carry out our work for the nation.

02:00:49.573 --> 02:00:51.541
Doesn't it bother you that you're stealing?

02:00:51.641 --> 02:00:53.541
Why?
Whose money is it?

02:00:53.643 --> 02:00:56.510
Mine today,
the moneylender's tomorrow.

02:00:56.613 --> 02:01:00.242
Why not use it for the cause?
-- No, Amulya.

02:01:00.350 --> 02:01:04.650
lf you go robbing treasuries,
l'll die of fear.

02:01:04.754 --> 02:01:07.018
Listen, you may not need
to sell all the jewelry.

02:01:07.123 --> 02:01:11.150
Sell as much as you need to
and bring back the rest.

02:01:12.162 --> 02:01:15.063
Take the box and carry it safely.

02:01:15.165 --> 02:01:18.066
And be careful, for heaven's sake.

02:01:19.002 --> 02:01:20.469
Very well, sister.

02:01:24.374 --> 02:01:26.740
l'll take my leave.
-- Okay.

02:01:50.767 --> 02:01:52.530
<i>Queen bee.</i>

02:02:02.212 --> 02:02:03.941
Are you leaving?

02:02:04.047 --> 02:02:06.311
ls there any reason for me to stay?

02:02:06.416 --> 02:02:08.407
Why do you say that?

02:02:08.518 --> 02:02:11.146
Can't you hear the note of discord?

02:02:12.188 --> 02:02:15.521
lf l've done anything wrong,
please forgive me.

02:02:15.625 --> 02:02:17.593
Don't leave like this.

02:02:18.128 --> 02:02:22.827
My husband said, ''The less one
knows you, the better one likes you''.

02:02:23.500 --> 02:02:26.264
Perhaps l know you too well.

02:02:26.369 --> 02:02:28.269
Don't say that, queen bee.

02:02:28.705 --> 02:02:31.435
Has knowing me meant nothing to you?

02:02:31.708 --> 02:02:33.608
Has it all been in vain?

02:02:33.710 --> 02:02:36.907
l believed you would
succeed in your endeavor.

02:02:37.013 --> 02:02:38.913
l wanted you to.

02:02:39.015 --> 02:02:41.279
But not anymore?

02:03:07.344 --> 02:03:09.938
<i>AIIah is great!</i>

02:04:04.034 --> 02:04:06.002
Kasim?

02:04:12.942 --> 02:04:14.409
Hands up.

02:04:17.280 --> 02:04:18.804
Hands up.

02:04:21.117 --> 02:04:22.311
Go inside.

02:04:22.419 --> 02:04:23.579
Go inside!

02:04:30.126 --> 02:04:31.320
Move.

02:04:33.797 --> 02:04:35.230
Turn around.

02:04:36.132 --> 02:04:37.724
Turn!

02:04:41.704 --> 02:04:43.638
Now open the safe.

02:04:44.307 --> 02:04:45.774
Open it!

02:04:50.814 --> 02:04:53.942
Take out 3,500 rupees.

02:04:54.717 --> 02:04:58.050
What's going on?
What's all the commotion?

02:04:58.321 --> 02:05:00.414
ls there a problem?

02:05:01.724 --> 02:05:03.453
l don't know.

02:05:04.127 --> 02:05:05.719
l hope it's not a riot.

02:05:05.829 --> 02:05:07.820
What are you saying?

02:05:08.164 --> 02:05:11.327
What will happen to us
if there's a riot here?

02:05:12.869 --> 02:05:15.064
We're going to Calcutta tomorrow.

02:05:15.905 --> 02:05:17.532
lt's no longer safe here.

02:05:17.640 --> 02:05:20.438
Who is ''we''?
Am l not coming with you?

02:05:23.213 --> 02:05:25.113
Did l say that?

02:05:27.217 --> 02:05:29.082
l'm so relieved.

02:05:29.185 --> 02:05:31.312
A treasury was looted nearby.

02:05:31.421 --> 02:05:34.288
What's to stop them from looting this place?

02:05:34.390 --> 02:05:38.053
lf they kill me, they'll burn my body
by that shriveled banyan tree.

02:05:38.161 --> 02:05:39.719
That would be awful.

02:05:41.664 --> 02:05:43.461
Go and get ready.

02:05:43.566 --> 02:05:45.397
Pack your things.

02:05:47.137 --> 02:05:49.401
You're serious about leaving, aren't you?

02:05:50.006 --> 02:05:52.031
l'm always serious.

02:05:53.076 --> 02:05:55.044
Don't you know me by now?

02:06:19.335 --> 02:06:21.030
Bimala?

02:06:23.840 --> 02:06:25.808
l have to tell you something.

02:06:25.909 --> 02:06:27.501
What is it?

02:06:27.777 --> 02:06:32.237
There were 5,000 rupees
in gold coins in two bags in the safe.

02:06:32.515 --> 02:06:34.449
l gave them to Sandip.

02:06:35.051 --> 02:06:36.985
He needed the money.

02:06:37.787 --> 02:06:41.689
Now you know how hard
it is to refuse him.

02:06:41.791 --> 02:06:43.190
l'll pay the money back.

02:06:43.693 --> 02:06:45.558
l gave Amulya my jewelry box.

02:06:45.662 --> 02:06:47.721
He'll sell my jewels and bring the money.

02:06:53.436 --> 02:06:58.635
l felt bad speaking to Sandip
like that in front of you.

02:07:01.077 --> 02:07:03.170
But l had to, Bimala.

02:07:04.180 --> 02:07:05.545
Things have taken a bad turn.

02:07:10.553 --> 02:07:13.488
lt's no longer safe for him to work here.

02:07:14.424 --> 02:07:16.949
But what about you?

02:07:20.663 --> 02:07:23.427
Your safety is what concerns me.

02:07:23.833 --> 02:07:27.428
No one else matters to me anymore.

02:07:28.238 --> 02:07:31.435
Tomorrow, we're going to Calcutta.

02:07:32.008 --> 02:07:33.737
All three of us.

02:07:34.777 --> 02:07:37.302
And if something happens before then?

02:07:40.250 --> 02:07:41.808
You won't leave the house, will you?

02:07:44.921 --> 02:07:48.448
lf something happens,
l'll have to go and intervene, Bimala.

02:07:53.263 --> 02:07:54.821
l knew it.

02:07:57.200 --> 02:08:00.431
l knew l'd be punished.

02:08:01.537 --> 02:08:03.971
l'll be punished.

02:08:07.143 --> 02:08:09.008
Punished? Why, Bimala?

02:08:09.879 --> 02:08:12.439
You haven't done anything wrong.

02:08:13.983 --> 02:08:18.852
l don't even have the right
to ask you for forgiveness.

02:08:21.090 --> 02:08:24.617
But you've come back to me,
haven't you?

02:08:25.862 --> 02:08:28.160
Haven't you, Bimala?

02:08:36.406 --> 02:08:41.105
lt seems like ages since l last
looked at you and spoke to you.

02:08:43.079 --> 02:08:45.172
What came over me?

02:08:45.915 --> 02:08:48.440
Why did this happen?

02:08:50.286 --> 02:08:52.083
You've done nothing wrong, Bimala.

02:08:53.122 --> 02:08:56.455
For ten years, you never saw
another man besides me.

02:08:58.361 --> 02:09:00.352
Don't forget that.

02:09:32.428 --> 02:09:34.623
There's 3,500 rupees here.

02:09:35.531 --> 02:09:38.762
Please return the jewelry box
and the gold coins.

02:09:40.036 --> 02:09:43.369
Where did you get that money?
Where have you been?

02:09:44.273 --> 02:09:46.264
To the treasury.

02:09:47.377 --> 02:09:48.605
l hope nobody saw you.

02:09:56.853 --> 02:09:58.718
l had my face covered.

02:09:59.055 --> 02:10:01.990
Did you see any trouble in the village?
-- There's a riot.

02:10:04.093 --> 02:10:07.290
The Muslims have broken
into the temple of Visalakshi.

02:10:17.774 --> 02:10:19.537
Are you leaving?

02:10:21.144 --> 02:10:22.771
Yes. To Rangpur.

02:10:28.117 --> 02:10:29.311
Will you come with me?

02:10:42.999 --> 02:10:44.398
l must go now.

02:10:52.675 --> 02:10:54.302
Hail Motherland.

02:11:10.860 --> 02:11:12.418
What are you thinking?

02:11:13.663 --> 02:11:15.324
Nothing.

02:11:16.999 --> 02:11:19.467
l don't want to think.

02:11:20.670 --> 02:11:22.763
l want to forget.

02:11:24.340 --> 02:11:27.503
Everything that's happened
in the last few days.

02:11:27.977 --> 02:11:30.878
Forget? But why?

02:11:30.980 --> 02:11:31.742
Nikhil!

02:11:35.284 --> 02:11:37.275
Come in, Sandip.

02:11:40.456 --> 02:11:42.686
This is the age of breaking rules.

02:11:43.426 --> 02:11:45.621
Your wife came out of her confinement,

02:11:45.728 --> 02:11:47.628
and now l've invaded
the privacy of your bedroom.

02:11:47.730 --> 02:11:49.664
l hope you'll forgive me.

02:11:52.134 --> 02:11:56.230
These are your property,
which l duly return.

02:11:57.006 --> 02:11:59.873
One jewelry box
and two bags of gold coins.

02:12:00.877 --> 02:12:02.344
The jewelry box?

02:12:03.112 --> 02:12:06.878
Your devotee didn't take it with him,
but he brought me the money.

02:12:10.286 --> 02:12:15.223
Since you have your valuables, l hope
you won't mind me keeping the money.

02:12:15.324 --> 02:12:17.622
-- Are you leaving?
-- Yes, Nikhil.

02:12:18.594 --> 02:12:21.222
The train to Rangpur leaves in an hour.

02:12:23.432 --> 02:12:26.731
Do you hear that?
The riots have started.

02:12:26.836 --> 02:12:28.565
Amulya saw them.

02:12:28.871 --> 02:12:33.467
And now l must make
my proverbial escape.

02:12:33.776 --> 02:12:35.107
l must live.

02:12:35.878 --> 02:12:38.108
l have a lot of work left to do.

02:12:38.381 --> 02:12:40.906
Don't make the same mistake again.

02:12:41.017 --> 02:12:43.281
Can't you see the results of your actions?

02:12:44.253 --> 02:12:46.448
l follow the <i>Bhagavadgita,</i> Nikhil.

02:12:46.722 --> 02:12:50.658
l am concerned only
with the action, not the result.

02:12:50.760 --> 02:12:55.060
And l consider Ravana to be
the hero of Ramayana, not Rama.

02:12:55.164 --> 02:12:58.099
So l can't accept advice
from the followers of Rama.

02:12:59.235 --> 02:13:01.135
The easy road isn't for me, Nikhil.

02:13:02.805 --> 02:13:04.500
l'll take my leave.

02:13:09.879 --> 02:13:11.972
This will stay with me.

02:13:17.286 --> 02:13:19.277
l'm keeping this as a memento.

02:13:20.289 --> 02:13:22.621
Who knows if we'll ever meet again?

02:13:25.394 --> 02:13:26.691
Good--bye, Nikhil.

02:13:31.400 --> 02:13:32.958
Queen bee.

02:13:39.041 --> 02:13:41.339
Hail Motherland.

02:14:17.013 --> 02:14:18.913
Courage, Bimala.

02:14:20.416 --> 02:14:23.977
l must go out to them now.
-- No! l won't let you!

02:14:24.086 --> 02:14:25.451
l must.

02:14:28.090 --> 02:14:29.853
Please don't stop me.

02:14:31.293 --> 02:14:32.851
My dear.

02:15:04.193 --> 02:15:07.094
-- You let him go?
-- We tried to stop him.

02:15:07.196 --> 02:15:08.891
He wouldn't listen to us!

02:15:10.232 --> 02:15:12.029
You witch!

02:15:12.735 --> 02:15:16.671
You sent him to his death!

02:15:17.306 --> 02:15:21.538
Have you no pity
in your heart of stone?
